  "title": "Beautician",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Job Title:</strong> Beautician</h2><p><strong>Company:</strong> TGK Beauty<br /><strong>Location:</strong> Singapore<br /><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Full-Time<br /><strong>Salary Range:</strong> SGD <strong>4,000 – 6,000</strong> (based on experience & performance)</p><h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><p>We are seeking a skilled and customer-focused <strong>Beautician</strong> to join our beauty team. The successful candidate will provide professional beauty treatments while delivering a comfortable and positive customer experience.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Perform professional facial treatments including deep cleansing and skin care</p></li><li><p>Provide hair spa and scalp care treatments</p></li><li><p>Carry out waxing treatments (e.g. honey waxing, ice/laser-based systems where applicable)</p></li><li><p>Conduct basic skin analysis and recommend suitable treatments</p></li><li><p>Maintain hygiene, cleanliness, and proper sanitisation of treatment rooms and tools</p></li><li><p>Deliver consistent service quality and excellent customer care</p></li><li><p>Follow company SOPs, safety guidelines, and service standards</p></li><li><p>Assist with basic customer scheduling and after-treatment advice</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Job Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Minimum 1<strong> years of relevant experience</strong> as a Beautician or similar role</p></li><li><p>Experience in <strong>facial treatments, waxing, and hair spa/scalp care</strong></p></li><li><p>Knowledge of basic skin care products and treatment techniques</p></li><li><p>Good communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Customer-oriented with a professional and responsible attitude</p></li><li><p>Willingness to work retail hours, including weekends and public holidays</p></li><li><p>Relevant beauty certifications or training will be an advantage</p></li></ul><h3><strong>How to Apply</strong></h3><p>Interested applicants may submit their resume via <strong>MyCareersFuture</strong></p>",
